thread.title: Keiran-Lee
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Keiran-Lee

author: Keiran-Lee
title: Keiran-Lee
text: I was really down n out after losing my job, i had no money coming in, just lost our accommodation and these guys stood by me all the way, they never harrassed me, never demanded payment was very appreciative of the way i was treated and they understood my circumstances after being with them for 12 months they even delivered my stuff to my new accommodation for FREE!!
